<Layout title="Privacy Policy – Hyperdaily">
  <section class="prose mx-auto py-10">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Last Updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}</p>

    <p>
      Hyperdaily (“we”, “our”, or “us”) is a daily trending blog that shares news,
      ideas, opinions, and insights on various topics including internet culture,
      business, lifestyle, and technology.
      This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your data
      when you visit and interact with our website.
    </p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>

    <h3>1. Information You Provide</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Name (if submitted through forms)</li>
      <li>Email Address (for contact or newsletter forms)</li>
      <li>Messages or inquiries you submit</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>2. Automatic Usage Data</h3>
    <p>When you browse our site, some information is collected automatically:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>IP Address</li>
      <li>Browser type & device type</li>
      <li>Pages visited & time spent</li>
      <li>General location (city/region)</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>3. Cookies & Third-Party Analytics</h3>
    <p>Hyperdaily uses cookies to improve user experience. We also use:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Google Analytics</strong> for traffic & performance insights</li>
      <li><strong>Google AdSense</strong> for displaying interest-based ads</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      Google and other advertisers may use cookies to show personalized ads.
      You may opt-out of personalized ads here:
      <br />
      <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads">https://www.google.com/settings/ads</a>
    </p>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To respond to inquiries</li>
      <li>To improve site content and user experience</li>
      <li>To show relevant and non-intrusive advertisements</li>
      <li>To analyze trends and understand audience interests</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>
      We <strong>do not sell</strong> your personal data.
      However, we share limited, non-identifiable usage data with:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Google (Analytics & AdSense)</li>
      <li>Form service providers (if you use our contact form)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Request deletion of your submitted information</li>
      <li>Request to stop future email contact</li>
      <li>Clear browser cookies to reset tracking preferences</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>
      For privacy concerns, requests, or general questions, you can reach us at:
      <br /><strong>Email:</strong> contact@hyperdaily.one
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
